data.body:
We're getting in the festive spirit early with our annual Big Advent Calendar Giveaway!&nbsp;

That's right, it's back for 2023!&nbsp;

Keep an eye on our social media pages from Monday &ndash; and all next week &ndash; as we'll be giving away some incredible advent calendars from brands you love!&nbsp;

A whole week of giveaways to help you get in the festive spirit! From fragrances to new experiences...

&nbsp;To be in it to win it:

&bull; Follow us on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/bluelightcarddiscounts">Facebook</a> and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bluelightcard">Instagram</a>

&bull; Look out for the competitions at 10am each day

&bull; Follow the entry rules in each post&nbsp;

Good luck!
